<ingredients><ingredient amount="0.5 Cup">Soy Sauce</ingredient><ingredient amount="0.5 Cup">Sugar</ingredient><ingredient amount="2.0 Tablespoon">Olive Oil</ingredient></ingredients>
<instructions>
In a medium bowl, mix ingredients together until well-combined.
Add marinade and steak to resealable container, and marinate steak until ready to cook.
